715256f-a.title: Manhattan: 122nd Street (East) - Lexington Avenue
715256f-a.text:
131-135 East 122nd Street, north side, west of Lexington Ave. The
frame houses shown, bear Nos. 131-133.
July 19, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
